@startuml afonsocastro_larcc_interface

skinparam componentStyle uml2

[UR10e Control Interface] as UR10e
[MoveIt! Integration] as MoveIt
[Robot Kinematics] as Kinematics
[LARCC Workcell Description] as Workcell
[RealSense Camera Support] as RealSense
[3D Model Definitions] as Models

cloud "ROS" {
  [ur_robot_driver]
  [realsense2_camera]
  [ur10e_moveit_config]
}

UR10e --> [ur_robot_driver]
RealSense --> [realsense2_camera]
MoveIt --> [ur10e_moveit_config]

Kinematics --> MoveIt : Provides IK/FK solvers
Workcell --> MoveIt : Defines work cell layout
Models --> Workcell : Provides 3D meshes

[ur_robot_driver] --> UR10e : Controls
[realsense2_camera] --> RealSense : Manages
[ur10e_moveit_config] --> MoveIt : Configures

@enduml